Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:32.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}拾起了somewhere　不知誰人掉落之物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:38.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}已被遺忘的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:46.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}撩起了　my那一點母性本能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:53.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}so　這應該不是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}有一個願望 決不退讓
